      <title>Topgolf 因担心分拆“来得太晚”而遭遇双重降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/topgolf-modg-hit-by-double-downgrade-on-fear-spinoff-comes-too-late</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Topgolf Callaway Brands Corp. 同名练习场的销售放缓以及沉重的债务负担有可能吓跑买家，促使雷蒙詹姆斯 (Raymond James) 大幅下调该公司的评级。]]></description>
